<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4619061>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 6. Distribution of Flagitopisa in the Philippine archipelago. Solid circles indicate known localities as follows: 1a) Flagitopisa philippensis—Type-locality, Luzon Island, near Los Baños, on the southern shore of Laguna de Bay; 1b) Luzon Island, in the Camarines Sur Province, approximately 240 km SE of the type locality; 1c) the island of Bohol, approximately 550 km SSE of the type locality; 2) Flagitopisa fluviatilis—Luzon Island, Laguna Province, Pagsanjan Falls." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4619061/files/figure.png" .

